    "The latter is expected to enrich the solution exploration by rewarding solution uniqueness, potentially leading to more robust and reliable WCET estimations.",
    "This inquiry is conducted across two case studies to assess the adaptability of the RL method to diverse applications and its effectiveness in complex problem-solving scenarios.",
    "The aim is to determine if integrating diversity into the reward system enhances the algorithm's performance and if so, in what ways.3.",
